#: ../../migration.md:1
msgid "Migration guide"
msgstr "迁移指南"

#: ../../migration.md:3
msgid "Koffi 1.x to 2.x"
msgstr "Koffi 1.x to 2.x"

#: ../../migration.md:5
msgid ""
"The API was changed in 2.x in a few ways, in order to reduce some "
"excessively \"magic\" behavior and reduce the syntax differences between "
"C and the C-like prototypes."
msgstr ""
"为了减少某些过度\"魔法\"的行为以及减少C和C风格原型之间的语法差异, API在2.x中发生了一些变更."

#: ../../migration.md:7
msgid "You may need to change your code if you use:"
msgstr "如果你使用了下列内容, 你可能需要更改你的代码:"

#: ../../migration.md:9
msgid "Callback functions"
msgstr "回调函数"

#: ../../migration.md:10
msgid "Opaque types"
msgstr "不透明类型"

#: ../../migration.md:11
msgid "`koffi.introspect()`"
msgstr "`koffi.introspect()`"

#: ../../migration.md:13
msgid "Callback type changes"
msgstr "回调类型更改"

#: ../../migration.md:15
msgid ""
"In Koffi 1.x, callbacks were defined in a way that made them usable "
"directly as parameter and return types, obscuring the underlying pointer."
" Now, you must use them through a pointer: `void CallIt(CallbackType "
"func)` in Koffi 1.x becomes `void CallIt(CallbackType *func)` in version "
"2.0 and newer."
msgstr ""
"在Koffi 1.x中, 回调被声明为可以直接作为参数和返回类型中使用, 隐藏了底层的指针. "
"现在, 你必须通过指针来使用它: Koffi 1.x中的`void CallIt(CallbackType func)`在Koffi 2.0及之后变成了`void CallIt(CallbackType *func)`."

