msgid ""
"The two versions below illustrate the API difference between Koffi 1.x "
"and Koffi 2.x:"
msgstr ""
"下列的两个版本展示了Koffi 1.x和Koffi 2.x的API区别:"

#: ../../migration.md:64
msgid ""
"Koffi 1.x only supported [transient callbacks](callbacks.md#javascript-"
"callbacks), you must use Koffi 2.x for registered callbacks."
msgstr ""
"Koffi 1.x仅支持[临时回调](callbacks.md#javascript-callbacks), 你必须升级到Koffi 2.x才能使用注册回调."

#: ../../migration.md:67
msgid ""
"The function `koffi.proto()` was introduced in Koffi 2.4, it was called "
"`koffi.callback()` in earlier versions."
msgstr ""
"Koffi 2.4引入了函数`koffi.proto()`, 在此之前的版本叫做`koffi.callback()`."

#: ../../migration.md:70
msgid "Opaque type changes"
msgstr "不透明类型更改"

#: ../../migration.md:72
msgid ""
"In Koffi 1.x, opaque handles were defined in a way that made them usable "
"directly as parameter and return types, obscuring the underlying pointer."
" Now, in Koffi 2.0, you must use them through a pointer, and use an array"
" for output parameters."
msgstr ""
"在Koffi 1.x中, 不透明句柄被声明为可以直接作为参数和返回类型中使用, 隐藏了底层的指针. "
"现在, 你必须通过指针来使用它们, 以及使用数组来作为输出参数."

#: ../../migration.md:74
msgid ""
"In addition to that, `koffi.handle()` has been deprecated in Koffi 2.1 "
"and replaced with `koffi.opaque()`. They work the same but new code "
"should use `koffi.opaque()`, the former one will eventually be removed in"
" Koffi 3.0."
msgstr ""
"除此之外, 你应该使用`koffi.opaque()`(Koffi 2.1引入)而非已经弃用, 将在Koffi 3.0中被移除的`koffi.handle()`."

