#: ../../migration.md:148
msgid "New koffi.introspect()"
msgstr "新的koffi.introspect()"

#: ../../migration.md:150
msgid ""
"In Koffi 1.x, `koffi.introspect()` would only work with struct types, and"
" return the object passed to `koffi.struct()` to initialize the type. Now"
" this function works with all types."
msgstr ""
"在Koffi 1.x中, `koffi.introspect()`只能被用于结构体类型, 且返回传入`koffi.struct()`的含有成员名称和类型的对象. "
"现在这个函数堆所有类型都可以工作."

